quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  69,9,"Fir'awna e mofte adinooɓe mo ɓen, e ca'e lettiranooɗe wayliteede ɗen, woni yimɓe Luutu ɓen, ɓe ardi e kuuɗe bonɗe immorde e sirku e geddi."
  69,10,"Kala maɓɓe yeddi Nulaaɗo mun on, ɓe fenni mo; Allah nanngiri ɓe nanngal ɓeydiingal ko O timminta halkude ɓe."
  69,11,"Ko Menen woni, fewndo ndiyam ɗam hummbunoo, ronndinoo ɓen wonunooɓe keeceele mon ka laana dogayka, ka Annabi Nuuhu lesunoo e yamiroore Amen, fii ko waɗɗoɗon e mun."
  69,12,"Men waɗiri kan laana e fillayee makka on, waaju ko dallinoree e halkeede yedduɓe ɓen, daɗnda gomɗimɓe ɓen, nowru nanayndu nana ɗum."
  69,13,"Si Malaa'ikaajo halfinaaɗo wuttugol on ka allaandu wuttii wuttaande wootere, ko ndeen woni ɗiɗaɓiire nden."
  69,14,"Leydi ndin e pelle ɗen ɓamtee, ɗe mo ɓññe mo ɓññannde sattunde, pecce leydi ndi e pelle ɗe sewi."
  69,15,"Nden ɗum fow waɗata, Darngal ngal daroo."
  69,16,"Kammu ngun seekora nden ñalnde, sabu jippagol Malaa'ika'en, hara hingu lo'i, ɓaawo ngu wonnde sattungu jogondirngu."
  69,17,"Hara Malaa'ika'en no wontiri ka seraaji maggu, njeetato e Malaa'ikaaɓe ɓannitaaɓe ɓen ronndoo Arsi Joomi maa kin nden ñalnde."
  69,18,"Nden ñalnde, ko onon weeɓitetee ka Allah, onon ɓee yimɓe. Hay huunde e fii mon suuɗotaako Mo. Allah ko ƴellitoto fii maɓɓe on fow."
  69,19,"Si ko jonnitiroyaaɗo talkuru golle mun ɗen ka ñaamo mun, on weltoroyay wi'ugol : Jaɓee ! Janngon talkuru golle am ɗen."
  69,20,"Min mi fellitu ka aduna, wonnde mi immmintinoyte, mi hawra e njoɓdi am ndin."
  69,21,"Hara himo e nguurndam welɗam, hakkee neema duumiiɗo ko o yi'ata."
  69,22,"E nder Aljanna toowuɗo nokku e darja."
  69,23,"Aljanna mo teɓateeriiji mun weli heɓude."
  69,24,"Ɓe teddiniree wi'aneede : ñaamee yariron ko lorra woo alaa e mu'un, sabu ko ardinirɗon kon golle moƴƴe e ñalaaɗe feƴƴunooɗe aduna."
  69,25,"Si tawii non ko jonnitiraaɗo talkuru golle mun ɗen ka nano mun, on wi'oyay : Ee bone am! Haananiino lam hara mi joniitaaka talkuru golle am ɗen, sabu kuuɗe bone ko woni e mayru kon, waɗata haa mi lettee."
  69,26,"Hara mi anndaali hay huunde e ko wonata ñaawoore am."
  69,27,"Hara maayde am nden wonuno timmoode am nde immintiŋtaake e mun fes."
  69,28,"Jawdi am ndin nafiraali lam duñangol lam lette Allah ɗen."
  69,29,"Cemmbe e jaahu am ko mi wallitoraynoo fow bonntirii lam."
  69,30,"Malaa'ika'en wi'anee : nanngee mo, kombon mo haa e daande."
  69,31,"Refti naadon mo ka Yiite fii no o meeɗira nguleendi magge."
  69,32,"Refti naadon mo e nder jolokooje ɗe junndi mun woni cappanɗe jeeɗiɗi sogonal."
  69,33,"Tawde pellet, o gomɗinaano Allah Mawɗo On."
  69,34,"O reerɗintaano woɗɓe goo e ñammingol miskiino."